  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">MUTIMA CENTRE HEALS TRAUMA AT SOUTH KIVU</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Coopera Congo provides psychosocial treatment to heal the collective trauma of South Kivu people and build their resilience in the face of conflict, epidemics, and natural disasters. The MUTIMA Psychosocial Reference Center is under construction. The center includes specialized services for the psychological and psychiatric treatment of adults and children.  With this project, we will build 4 therapy rooms, hire 4 psychologists, and train them to care for 400 people per month.</narrative>
  </description>
